{"id": 1757, "genre": 1001, "title": "在你居住的城市，你觉得有什么看起来风光但并不实用的设计？", "description": "难用，又难以理解。", "record_count": 4676, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201706251150391oK6LsCN8UpwBgOc.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-06-26T03:00:58Z", "options": [{"id": 216064, "content": "人行横道红绿灯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 514176}, {"id": 217088, "content": "分类垃圾桶:无论分得多细，都是一起处理的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979454}, {"id": 216066, "content": "美丽的行道树，夏天不遮荫，只负责冬天掉叶子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1063960}, {"id": 216067, "content": "为了禁止开墙打洞把街边所有的小店都拆干净", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1063965}, {"id": 216323, "content": "国家大剧院", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 867975}, {"id": 216068, "content": "西安-国家旅游城市-然后一年到晚空气差的上新闻联播，可笑至极", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 847419}, {"id": 216324, "content": "学校前面公园的长廊亭很阴暗，他们一直说像灵堂……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056538}, {"id": 216580, "content": "高高挂起的公交小站牌和不亮路号灯的公交车", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1065024}, {"id": 216069, "content": "拆了城市独一无二的标志性华表，建音乐喷泉（然而我们已经有了一个）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 603551}, {"id": 216583, "content": "没有公用电话的公用电话亭？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1065012}, {"id": 219144, "content": "超豪华的政府大楼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026373}, {"id": 216078, "content": "hh\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054420}, {"id": 217102, "content": "艳阳天里几乎没有一棵树的超级大广场。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1065732}, {"id": 220686, "content": "杨树 一到夏天就吹杨树毛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076061}, {"id": 216079, "content": "一幢又一幢的高楼楼顶", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056653}, {"id": 216080, "content": "学校篮球场 很少有篮球课", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1063991}, {"id": 216084, "content": "所有街道都长的一样。每个破烂的地方外围都修了白墙灰瓦南方小巷的样子，里面却在霉烂生蛆。像极了现在的国。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321342}, {"id": 216086, "content": "天府广场中间那个。【逃】", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 749248}, {"id": 216087, "content": "红色纪念，主题思想宣传栏", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680656}, {"id": 218647, "content": "刚铺好了一条街的地砖，过不了多久又掀开，又换了一种地砖铺上…彰显换领导？还是这种烂操作，无fuck说。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1063693}, {"id": 216093, "content": "共享单车，一个连自行车道都没几条的城市要这东西干啥。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054488}, {"id": 216094, "content": "成都三环路主道和辅道转换的进出口，栽满了乔灌木，不是应该提前二三十米就不栽了么…这样很挡视线", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475629}, {"id": 216863, "content": "分类的垃圾桶，自从有了它我一直分类，直到我看到了清洁工把垃圾倒在同一个垃圾桶里。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1065431}, {"id": 216098, "content": "天安门", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 484525}, {"id": 216099, "content": "泉城之根？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1048069}, {"id": 216100, "content": "空无一人的商品房", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921594}, {"id": 216101, "content": "两座楼间的路是斜的，要多走好远…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1064040}, {"id": 216102, "content": "上海中心利用率很低", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 797440}, {"id": 216358, "content": "全省最高的地标性建筑物…据说没钱盖了…不封顶…无限期搁置…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 933050}, {"id": 216103, "content": "走断腿的机场", "image": null, "praise_count": 68, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050868}, {"id": 216104, "content": "空空如也的博物馆", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1062238}, {"id": 216618, "content": "县城里无比巨大的高铁动车站广场。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1065100}, {"id": 216107, "content": "廣州珠江新城嘅花城匯廣場負層綜合體。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690175}, {"id": 216109, "content": "我是来看评论的\r\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166753}, {"id": 216878, "content": "佛罗伦萨小镇，欧洲小镇，欧罗巴风情商业街……当你真去过欧洲你会骂娘，那设计的是什么鬼……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935385}, {"id": 219184, "content": "城市立交桥，经常堵塞，还说是为了分担道路交通压力而建的，可是建了以后桥上和地下的车流量一样，多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1070060}, {"id": 216881, "content": "行政中心的前台阶，永远是高不可攀，且大部分没有无障碍通道，做轮子的各位请走车行道", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935385}, {"id": 218417, "content": "BRT绝对是它，对一个三线却又是首府的城市来说，不建说不过去，建了满满槽点", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1046680}, {"id": 219185, "content": "女骑警", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 985410}, {"id": 220209, "content": "天空树", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671476}, {"id": 220465, "content": "堵了半个城的BRT", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1075627}, {"id": 220467, "content": "政府", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1041422}, {"id": 220725, "content": "各种商业中心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076114}, {"id": 217399, "content": "地铁站的保护大象标语…买象牙的人要成天挤地铁吗？给谁看啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 910973}, {"id": 222009, "content": "行人红绿灯等待时间缩短按钮", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1070588}, {"id": 216122, "content": "核心价值观及各种口号，宣传栏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 976286}, {"id": 222010, "content": "行人红绿灯等待时间缩短按钮，好像高大上，并没有什么用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1070588}, {"id": 216123, "content": "我们大学的校门，只是用来骗新生的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1062057}, {"id": 216124, "content": "修路修路 不知道怎么出门", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 818230}, {"id": 216125, "content": "共享单车电瓶车扰乱了正常的道路和整齐的风景线....尤其是横贯马路的电瓶车真的会吓死司机和正常的路人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1008051}]}